'<a href="http://csteachingtips.org/tip/ensure-equitable-access-your-classroom-don%E2%80%99t-allow-language-reinforcing-idea-computer-science-">To ensure equitable access in your classroom, don’t allow language reinforcing the idea that computer science is “guy stuff” in the classroom, even passively.</a>',
